349
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:20,000
There's no need.

350
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:23,900
I know it's really hard to get a reservation at this restaurant.

351
00:25:24,700 --> 00:25:26,400
How about this?

352
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:30,600
If I help you get a good job, then you can invite me to a meal.

353
00:25:30,600 --> 00:25:32,600
If I ate this meal with you today,

354
00:25:32,600 --> 00:25:35,600
I would feel in debt to you.

355
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:37,800
Goodbye.

356
00:25:37,800 --> 00:25:39,400
Goodbye.

357
00:26:10,600 --> 00:26:13,400
 I'm done here, where are we meeting? 

358
00:26:25,800 --> 00:26:27,700
 Hidden Prosperity 

359
00:26:27,700 --> 00:26:29,200
 You can come straight here. 

360
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:31,200
 I'm already here. 

361
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:39,100
Hello, Miao Miao's mother.

362
00:26:39,100 --> 00:26:41,400
- You're so early. 
 - I didn't have any other business, so I figured I should come early.

363
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:44,000
