416
00:29:31,600 --> 00:29:34,800
Sister Ziru took the initiative to offer to help.

417
00:29:34,800 --> 00:29:37,000
I couldn't say no.

418
00:29:38,600 --> 00:29:42,000
So you are at ease with letting her shoulder the burden

419
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:46,200
