422
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:02,600
It's so much money though.

423
00:30:02,600 --> 00:30:05,600
How many TVs would I have to sell to make it all back?

424
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:12,500
Siyu,

425
00:30:13,910 --> 00:30:16,070
didn't I tell you?

426
00:30:16,100 --> 00:30:19,400
I can pay this off for you.

427
00:30:21,800 --> 00:30:24,200
Your money doesn't grow on trees either.

428
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:27,000
You worked hard for it.

429
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:30,500
But at least it will give me peace of mind.

430
00:30:44,600 --> 00:30:47,200
It's so much money!

431
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:57,700
I suggest we focus more on...

432
00:30:57,700 --> 00:31:01,000
- Let me take this call. 
 - ...the technology behind batteries.

433
00:31:05,800 --> 00:31:09,300
- Hello? 
 - Sister Ziru, do you have time tomorrow?

434
00:31:09,300 --> 00:31:11,200
What's going on, Siyu?

435
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:13,300
I want to treat you to a meal.

436
00:31:13,300 --> 00:31:16,900
I think I should pay for the car's repair.

437
00:31:16,900 --> 00:31:21,000
I'll take you up on the meal offer, but let's not talk about the car repair anymore.

438
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:22,800
Do you have time tomorrow?

439
00:31:22,800 --> 00:31:25,800
Sure. Once you've made the reservation just send me the address.

440
00:31:25,800 --> 00:31:28,300
It's a deal. I'll see you tomorrow.

441
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:35,200
Your annual salary isn't that high.

442
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:39,400
Why do you think you can make back this money in one year?

443
00:31:39,400 --> 00:31:41,400
I'm amazing.

444
00:31:42,700 --> 00:31:45,200
I... I have a plan.

445
00:31:45,200 --> 00:31:48,700
I have a plan to get the company to give me a raise.

446
00:31:50,600 --> 00:31:53,900
Then I wish you a smooth promotion and salary raise.

447
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:56,900
Thanks.

448
00:32:02,400 --> 00:32:04,600
Go with me tomorrow.

449
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:07,000
Sure.

450
00:32:08,300 --> 00:32:10,800
[You are here]

451
00:32:11,600 --> 00:32:14,500
[I am here]

452
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:21,200
