453
00:32:23,600 --> 00:32:26,300
[Work hard for your dream]

454
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:34,900
She said she's willing to accompany me.

455
00:32:35,600 --> 00:32:38,600
People even break contracts that are written on paper.

456
00:32:38,600 --> 00:32:41,400
This is just an oral promise.

457
00:32:42,100 --> 00:32:44,900
Li Siyu wouldn't do such a thing.

458
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:49,900
Then let me ask you. When you wanted to divide the team today,

459
00:32:49,900 --> 00:32:52,100
why didn't she agree?

460
00:32:55,800 --> 00:32:58,000
 This time I will be running beside you. 

461
00:32:58,800 --> 00:33:00,600
Sit down.

462
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:04,300
Siyu, take a look at this.

463
00:33:04,300 --> 00:33:07,000
These are the names of everyone in our Sales Department.

464
00:33:07,000 --> 00:33:08,700
Pick some.

465
00:33:08,700 --> 00:33:11,100
I'm picking?

466
00:33:11,100 --> 00:33:13,400
If you're going to be the Team Two's leader, then you need to have people in your team.

467
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:15,200
Besides the people who have always been with you,

468
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:19,400
Xia Xiaotian, Liu Xiaojia, look at some others.

469
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:23,600
These people have always

470
00:33:23,600 --> 00:33:27,000
been with me, so they will stay with me.

471
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:31,300
- This one, this one.
- Sister Yuan, the company says that the decision must be mutual.

