473
00:33:33,600 --> 00:33:35,500
Just let them make their own choice.

474
00:33:35,500 --> 00:33:39,600
Wouldn't that just create a mess? What if they all pick to be on my team?

475
00:33:39,600 --> 00:33:41,200
Or all pick to be in your team?

476
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:44,100
First of all, they probably wouldn't pick me.

477
00:33:44,100 --> 00:33:46,400
There's always a first-come, first-served process.

478
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:50,600
If your team is full, then even if someone wanted to get in, they can't.

