00:34:15,200 --> 00:34:16,600
- Good morning, Sister Siyu. 
 - Good morning.

483
00:34:16,600 --> 00:34:18,700
- Good morning. 
 - Good morning.

484
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:25,000
Sis, Lin Ling asked if our team still has room for more people.

485
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:27,500
She says she wants to join our team.

486
00:34:27,500 --> 00:34:29,000
Lin Ling?

